commit_message:
Augment Mysql status checking for replication

Augments the MysqlAppStatus class to report replication slave
status.  Adds two new status states:
	DETACHED - slave is running, but not connected to master
	DELAYED - slave is lagging master site changes

Partially implements: blueprint replication-v1

Change-Id: Ib64d3e02ad8422aea9e95e6ddd9aa058a4039a1c

commit_message:
Add mgmt API for datastores

Implemented API calls and shell commands for create/update
datastores/versions.

DocImpact: added CLI for datastores version management
Depends-On: I01c0ecc276a73fbbc06ec39bfaa1c66f47fc3a9c Trove

Change-Id: Iee7ed7b141548ef64231acad6319e769d356b97f
Partially Implements: blueprint datastores-mgmt-api

Thank you for your first contribution to OpenStack.

    Your patch will now be tested automatically by OpenStack testing frameworks
    and once the automatic tests pass, it will be reviewed by other friendly
    developers. They will give you feedback and may require you to refine it.

    People seldom get their patch approved on the first try, so don't be
    concerned if requested to make corrections. Feel free to modify your patch
    and resubmit a new change-set.

    Patches usually take 3 to 7 days to be reviewed so be patient and be
    available on IRC to ask and answer questions about your work. The more you
    participate in the community the more rewarding it is for you. You may also
    notice that the more you get to know people and get to be known, the faster
    your patches will be reviewed and eventually approved. Get to know others
    and become known by doing code reviews: anybody can do it, and it's a
    great way to learn the code base.

    Thanks again for supporting OpenStack, we look forward to working with you.

commit_message:
Incorrect error message- user-access-revoke API

Reason:
- In current code while revoking access of an user
from a schema. There is a check,
to find if user is associated
with a particular schema or not.
On failure of this check,
it raises an error DatabaseNotFound.
Which is incorrect,
because a proper error message should be
user does not have access on Database.

Changes:
- Added an exception UserAcessRightsNotFound indicating
that user does not have access on particular DB.

Change-Id: Iff9550c084dc33326d817f195f7f04232a30fa2d
Closes-Bug: #1302405

commit_message:
Add mgmt API for datastores

Implemented mgmt API calls for create/update datastores/versions.
To access this API call "admin" role is required.
Removed datastores related commands from trove-manage.
Changed response from datastore-list, now regular user can see only
datastores which has atleast one active version.

Needed-By: I01c0ecc276a73fbbc06ec39bfaa1c66f47fc3a9c
Needed-By: I49195c2c8c08fe4673b2dc69d86ea16ee7654431
Needed-By: Ia8ba15ff06c47cb46d68472b336b8ffc1a5e9722

Change-Id: I01c0ecc276a73fbbc06ec39bfaa1c66f47fc3a9c
Implements: blueprint datastores-mgmt-api

commit_message:
Add notifications for trove.instance.resize.*.* actions

Reasons:
 - Trove should emit notifications when resources are being used.

Changes:
 - added instance.resize.flavor usage notifications:
  - trove.instance.resize.flavor.start|end|error:
    - start|error|end emited by taskmanager;
 - added instance.resize.volume usage notifications:
  - trove.instance.resize.volume.start|end|error:
    - start|error|end emited by taskmanager;
 - unit/int tests proposed.

Partially Implements: blueprint ceilometer-integration

Change-Id: I6e003517824d5c854662d4ae1ef61a2232367995

commit_message:
Add notifications for trove.instance.* actions

Reasons:
 - Trove should emit notifications at certain stages.

Changes:
 - adding instance.:
   - create.start|end|error;
   - delete.start|end|error;
 - adding tests.

Partially Implements: blueprint ceilometer-integration

Change-Id: I8c56b033679bbae95bd28693b3bed3a87926a5b4

commit_message:
Extends datastore capability overrides and adds management cmds

Added trove management commands for adding and removing capabilities and
capabily overrrides.  Relocated capability-related test setup/teardown
from TestDatastoreBase into TestCapabilities class.

Change-Id: I997ef248ef2b9e42ff0c35efea4dca737c41e84f
Partially-Implements: blueprint capabilities

commit_message:
Add notifications for trove.backup.* actions

Reasons:
 - Trove should emit notifications when resources are being used.

Changes:
 - added backup usage notifications:
  - trove.backup.create.start|end|error:
    - start|error emited by taskmanager;
    - end|error emited by conductor.
  - trove.backup.delete.start|end|error:
    - all messages are emited by taskmanager.
 - unit/int tests proposed.

Partially Implements: blueprint ceilometer-integration

Change-Id: I8e7dbdb82e4a200f338c4273eeacbfc7d87c603f
